content: प्रसु-सू {c1c} <ab>P.</ab> {c2c} {c4c} <ab>A.</ab> {@--1@} To beget, generate, produce. {@--2@} To bring forth, be delivered of; पुत्ररत्नं प्रासोष्ट.

प्रसू {%<ab>a.</ab>%} Bringing forth, bearing, giving birth to; स्त्रीप्रसूश्चाधिवेत्तव्या <ls>Y. 1. 73.</ls> {%--<ab>f.</ab>%} {@--1@} A mother; मातरपितरौप्रसूजनयितारौ <ls>Ak.</ls> ‘parents’. {@--2@} A mare. {@--3@} A spreading creeper. {@--4@} A young shoot, tender grass.
